# PaunClip environment example
# ============================
# Keep your real `.env` in the repo root: `yt-short-clipper/.env`
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your own local values.

# OpenAI API key (optional if you configure providers through config.json/UI)
# OPENAI_APIKEY=sk-your-api-key-here

# Optional: custom output directory
# OUTPUT_DIR=./output

# Optional: default number of clips
# DEFAULT_NUM_CLIPS=5

# Optional: Whisper model size if you wire local Whisper later
# WHISPER_MODEL=base

# Optional: local cookies file location if you choose to wire env-based runtime paths
# COOKIES_FILE=./cookies.txt
